[SHORT DESC]
Effects vary with terrain.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Effects vary with terrain. Has a 30% chance to have the given effect associated with each terrain on the target. Wi-Fi is forced Building.</p>

<h3>Union Room / Wi-Fi</h3>
<dl>
<dt>Road</dt>
<dd>Lowers Accuracy 1 stage</dd>
<dt>Desert</dt>
<dd>Lowers Accuracy 1 stage</dd>
<dt>Building</dt>
<dd>Paralyzes</dd>
<dt>Grass</dt>
<dd>Sleep</dd>
<dt>Tall grass</dt>
<dd>Sleep</dd>
<dt>Cave</dt>
<dd>Flinches</dd>
<dt>Mountain</dt>
<dd>Flinches</dd>
<dt>Snow</dt>
<dd>Freezes </dd>
<dt>Pond</dt>
<dd>Lowers Attack 1 stage</dd>
<dt>Ocean</dt>
<dd>Lowers Attack 1 stage</dd>
</dl>

